data.description: Need more space?! This functional floor plan features a warm, welcoming interior and comprises a separate dining room, 6 well-proportioned bedrooms, relaxed living spaces and a bonus room. Enjoy the indoor/outdoor lifestyle in your tranquil backyard which includes patio dining space and covered deck. A true outdoor paradise. Perfectly positioned in a peaceful Rapides Parish neighborhood. This neighborhood is a desired choice for buyers thanks to its rural setting and easy access to great schools. Schedule your showing today!
